OL,3,CGuernsey Police Chief defends team
OL,4,Cafter leaked CCTV sparks criticism
OL,6,FRuari Hardy explains: "More staff
OL,7,Fdealing with a violent individual
OL,8,Fmakes it safer because they can
OL,9,Fcontrol the head, they can control the
OL,10,Flimbs and they can stop an attempt to
OL,11,Fbe violent.
OL,13,F"They can stop the offender from
OL,14,Fcommitting further assault by taking
OL,15,Fcontrol.
OL,17,F"It is about context and that is the
OL,18,Fissue we are seeing on social media.
OL,19,FAll too often, it's been spun in a way
OL,20,Fthat is as if we've done something
OL,21,Fhorrendously wrong.
