OL,3,CGuernsey Police Chief defends team
OL,4,Cafter leaked CCTV sparks criticism
OL,6,F"That individual had been involved in
OL,7,Fa very serious assault where a member
OL,8,Fof our community had been seriously
OL,9,Finjured. Officers had to restrain and
OL,10,Farrest the individual and some had to
OL,11,Fuse considerable restraint to arrest
OL,12,Fhim.
OL,14,F"Our officers still have a duty of
OL,15,Fcare to look after him, but because of
OL,16,Fthe threats to cause self-harm, the
OL,17,Fofficers were compelled to put him
OL,18,Finto clothing that didn't pose a
OL,19,Fligature risk and that is the section
OL,20,Fof the video that has been circulating
OL,21,Fonline."
