OL,3,CGuernsey Police Chief defends team
OL,4,Cafter leaked CCTV sparks criticism
OL,6,FAn investigation is ongoing into how
OL,7,Fthe CCTV footage was leaked.
OL,9,FSpeaking more widely, Mr Hardy does
OL,10,Fadmit that previous officers have
OL,11,F"fallen well below the standards,
OL,12,Findeed to a criminal level of
OL,13,Fbehaviour".
OL,15,FHe continues: "Criticism is valid and
OL,16,Fas the head of this organisation, I do
OL,17,Facknowledge that there are times when
OL,18,Four quality of service or level of
OL,19,Fservice falls below what the public
OL,20,Fexpects."
