OL,3,CGuernsey Police Chief defends team
OL,4,Cafter leaked CCTV sparks criticism
OL,6,FMr Hardy adds: "Officers are concerned
OL,7,Fthat they are being threatened with a
OL,8,Fnumber of civil and other complaints
OL,9,Fissues. However, we do everything we
OL,10,Fcan to maintain the integrity of what
OL,11,Fwe do.
OL,13,F"The volume and level of the criticism
OL,14,Fthat is currently being experienced on
OL,15,Fsocial media is placing the
OL,16,Forganisation in a position where the
OL,17,Fpublic perception could be impacted.
