OL,3,CGuernsey Police Chief defends team
OL,4,Cafter leaked CCTV sparks criticism
OL,6,F"We do a challenging job and the fact
OL,7,Fthat we go out 365 days a year to deal
OL,8,Fwith sometimes extreme violence, some
OL,9,Fvery difficult offences, my staff need
OL,10,Fto know they are supported.
OL,12,F"We are a community and social media
OL,13,Fhas a very valid place within the
OL,14,Fcommunity when it is used for good,
OL,15,Fbut when it is used for a consistent
OL,16,Fnegative campaign that is
OL,17,Finappropriate.
